<subSubSection box="[199,1335,1689,1714]" pageId="1" pageNumber="186" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1041,1822]" box="[199,1335,1689,1714]" pageId="1" pageNumber="186">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1689,1714]" pageId="1" pageNumber="186">Etymology.</emphasis>
The masculine generic name is named for the 
<typeStatus box="[856,904,1690,1714]" pageId="1" pageNumber="186">type</typeStatus>
